Vendored locations
------------------

nerf-mac-capture/  -- samply/src/mac/* (selected leaf-level Mach utilities;
                      higher-level capture pipeline incrementally)
nerf-mac-preload/  -- samply-mac-preload/* (DYLD_INSERT_LIBRARIES shim)

The bootstrap-server environment variable in nerf-mac-preload was renamed
SAMPLY_BOOTSTRAP_SERVER_NAME -> NERF_BOOTSTRAP_SERVER_NAME so the dylib
does not collide with a samply install.
